# Styling

- Palette: `#FFFFFF` background, `#000000` text/borders, red/orange accent for active states.
- `border: 1px solid #000`; `border-radius: 0` on buttons and cards.
- Sidebar + main two-column layout; feed grouped by date headers.
- Card header: solid black bar, white uppercase type label, timestamp right-aligned.
- No Tailwind/shadcn unless already adopted in the repo.
- Prefer CSS variables in `src/styles/tokens.css` for colors and spacing.
